The Gift of the Givers is stepping in to help the people of Touwsrivier in the Western Cape. It noticed a serious lack of medical supplies at a clinic in the small town. It means even something as simple but debilitating as a toothache can go untreated for weeks. eNCA's Nobesuthu Hejana is following the developments. Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - The Gift of the Givers is stepping in to help the people of Touwsrivier in the Western Cape. READ: Gift of the Givers supplying food to some EC hospitals It noticed a serious lack of medical supplies at a clinic in the small town. It means even something as simple but debilitating as a toothache can go untreated for weeks. Watch the video above for more details.